    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute stunner, and let me tell you\u2014it's basically in showroom condition! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It looks and drives like a total dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
