    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of the 997.2 generation, featuring the robust 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) naturally aspirated flat-six. This collector-grade example is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package, the vehicle offers exceptional lateral dynamics and throttle response. The exterior maintains its factory-original depth with zero swirl marks, while the undercarriage remains pristine, showing no signs of heat cycling or environmental wear. A comprehensive service dossier accompanies this mechanically superlative, concours-ready 911.",
