    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and retains its original, mirror-finish factory paint with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in showroom state; the premium leather bolsters show zero wear, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a thick folder of records to prove it. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. It sits on a fresh set of top-tier performance tires and needs nothing but a new curator. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 43500.0,
